The evidence with the title 'Barack Obama - Wikipedia ' says Barack Hussein Obama ii is an American attorney and politician who served as the 44th president of the United States from 2009 to 2017. A member of the Democratic Party, he was the first African American to be elected to the presidency. He previously served as a senator from Illinois from 2005 to 2008.  ...  ... By the time of his Senate run in 2004, he said that he supported civil unions ... 
